Merck KGaA Spoke With Ex-Minister Mappus About Role

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-07-27T09:28:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/merck-kgaa-spoke-with-ex-minister-mappus-about-role-correct-.html
(Corrects nature of role in first paragraph.)  Merck KGaA (MRK)  spoke with Stefan Mappus,
former minister president of the German state Baden-
Wuerttemberg, about a possible role with the company, Chief
Executive Officer Karl-Ludwig Kley said today on a conference
call. Kley declined to comment on what role that could be.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in London at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
